			<br/>
			A few Hammer and Dual Swords attacks will never make your hunter bounce, though the sound and particle effects will still play, and sharpness is reduced by two hits all the same. These include the Hammer Spins, combo Golf Swing, Golf Swing after spinning, and both components of the Superpound, and the Dual Swords Fury Combo.
		</p>

