		<h3>Motion Values</h3>
		<p>
			Bowguns calculate raw damage based on ammo MVs. Some shots can hit a target multiple times, and some shots also deal additional effects:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Pierce Shot will hit a monster at least once, and up to the maximum number of impacts in a straight line, unless it exits the monster sooner.</li>
			<li>Pellet Shot will hit all monsters in the cone of effect multiple times in quick succession; the number of impacts is higher the closer the monster is to the hunter and the center of the cone; all monsters in the cone take the full number of impacts regardless of any other monsters or hunters in the cone with them; Pellet shot is also not affected by physical obstructions.</li>
			<li>Clust Shot spawns a number of bomblets on impact, which scatter and explode on impact with any solid object.</li>
			<li>Flame, Water, and Thunder shot deal element damage as MV. Pellet, Crag, Clust and Dragon shot deal flat element damage.</li>
			<li>Shots with Ricochet will deal damage and change direction on impacting a monster; if it hits the monster again, it will deal full damage and ricochet again until reaching the maximum number of possible impacts (defined per shot below) or missing the monster.</li>
